# jspm-systemjs-angular-1x
A demo of using JSPM, SystemJS and Angular 1.4

### Installation
1. npm install
2. jspm install
3. gulp build [--dev] [--prod] [--vendor] [--templates]
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
